data.description: COMPLETELY RENOVATED  This beautiful 3 bed 2 bath home is located in mid city and features an open layout with plenty space for entertaining. This upscale renovation shows off luxury vinyl tile with beautiful grey custom cabinets with quartz counter tops that boost white with hints of grey in it to accentuate the high end backsplash, the large island easily accommodates entertaining any large gathering, or just having a few friends over. As you move through the home you will see the washer and dryer are tucked away just off the foyer. All of the bedrooms feature walk-in closets and all very nice size and have plenty of storage room. The additional bathroom has elegant gold touches and give off a spa like atmosphere. In the master ensuite you will see double vanities
